# PHI / sensitive data

Resume and intake data are sensitive (healthcare staffing context).

- Do not log full resume text, emails, phones, or license numbers in server console in production flows.
- Avoid returning raw `parsed_resume` blobs to the client unless required.
- Keep privacy copy on upload step accurate (placement only; not sold).
- Prefer server-side storage (Supabase `resumes` bucket) over client retention of file bytes.

When adding analytics or error reporting, strip PII from payloads.
